<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4551856>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 5. Classification tree from the CART analysis built on 60 individuals representing the four clades within the E. fornicatus complex. Relevant characters for the node splits are shown.Classification rates are expressed as the number of correct classifications divided by the number of observations (individual beetles) in the node for the individuals used to train the CART model." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4551856/files/figure.png" .

